&lt;li&gt;Perform engineering hand calculations and analysis to size structures and mechanisms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create detailed models and engineering prints in SolidWorks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and prototype systems in the lab&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with cross-disciplinary engineering teams to drive software-hardware co-design&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and build test equipment for both subsystem and complete system tests&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
